do Global.mod_can_move(false)
valen: Hello, void.
valen: Most of us down here are content with our lives.
valen: The Zenith can't corrupt us. You are safe here.
valen: Though do be warned...
valen: Other areas may not be like this...
valen: ...and what lies down below us is something not even the Zenith dares to touch.
valen: Nobody knows what it is, and no one has returned from those depths.
do Global.mod_can_move(true)